PROCEDURE TO CANCEL PENDING ORDERS DURING
SYSTEM FAILURE:
In case of IBTS System Failure due to any Reason from Investor’s
Part, Broker’s Part or 3rd Party Software Vendor’s Part, Investor
can call and talk to the KATS operator of the Broker to get update
regarding his/her lined up Orders, Can give Instructions to KATS
Operator to Cancel Orders or to line up further orders on his/her
Behalf or any amendment thereof:
Contact Details of the Brokers are as under:
